{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/kotlin-outline/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h3>1. Kotlin 이란?</h3>\n<p>JVM 기반의 언어이며 Java와 유사하지만 더 간결한 문법과 다양한 기능을 추가한 언어이다.\r\nJava와의 상호 운용이 100% 지원되므로 Java에 익숙한 개발자도 쉽게 접근할 수 있고\r\n안드로이드, 스프링 프레임워크 등에서도 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3>2. Java 쓰지 왜 굳이 Kotlin을 사용하는가?</h3>\n<p>Java와는 달리 간결한 문법에 유용한 기능 특히 Null 관련 처리를 안전하고 편하게 처리할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2>간결한 문법</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><pre class=\"language-kotlin\"><code class=\"language-kotlin\"><span class=\"token comment\">// getters, setters, equals(), hashCode(), toString(), copy()를 한 줄로 선언 가능</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">data</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token function\">Course</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">val</span> id <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Int<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">val</span> name <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> String<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">val</span> author <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> String<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Null 처리</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><pre class=\"language-kotlin\"><code class=\"language-kotlin\"><span class=\"token comment\">//형변환이 실패하는 모든 경우에 대해 안전하게 null을 반환해준다.</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> String <span class=\"token comment\">// null</span>\r\n<span class=\"token string-literal singleline\"><span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> File <span class=\"token comment\">// null</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">//as는 경우에 따라 kotlin.TypeCastException이나 java.lang.ClassCastException 예외를 발생시킬 수 있다</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> File <span class=\"token comment\">// kotlin.TypeCastException 예외 발생</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> File<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// null</span>\r\n<span class=\"token string-literal singleline\"><span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> File <span class=\"token comment\">// java.lang.ClassCastException 예외 발생</span>\r\n<span class=\"token string-literal singleline\"><span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> File<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// java.lang.ClassCastException 예외 발생</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2>Source</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/docs/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://kotlinlang.org/docs/home.html</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://developer.android.com/codelabs/basic-android-kotlin-compose-first-program?hl=ko#0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://developer.android.com/codelabs/basic-android-kotlin-compose-first-program?hl=ko#0</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://namu.wiki/w/Kotlin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://namu.wiki/w/Kotlin</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Kotlin 개요","summary":"코틀린은 무엇이며 왜 사용하는가? 자바랑 무슨 차이가 있는가?","date":"2023.06.15.","categories":["Kotlin"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9cae29c6c03a3c6c978bf74ecf9fef05/04635/kotlin-img.png","srcSet":"/static/9cae29c6c03a3c6c978bf74ecf9fef05/45daf/kotlin-img.png 63w,\n/static/9cae29c6c03a3c6c978bf74ecf9fef05/fbd2a/kotlin-img.png 125w,\n/static/9cae29c6c03a3c6c978bf74ecf9fef05/04635/kotlin-img.png 250w","sizes":"(min-width: 250px) 250px, 100vw"},"source